// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1593 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b2af996f-4985-54af-bad9-03aef981a169

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
